  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-10o75c2\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\"></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-fe75629d2952827e78801ee490a87fcc_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"640\" data-rawheight=\"640\" data-original-token=\"v2-bbbbcd707227476753c509e25055c48e\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-41badebbdd597c0dac7808eecda13a31_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"640\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-fe75629d2952827e78801ee490a87fcc_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='640' height='640'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"640\" data-rawheight=\"640\" data-original-token=\"v2-bbbbcd707227476753c509e25055c48e\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-41badebbdd597c0dac7808eecda13a31_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"640\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-fe75629d2952827e78801ee490a87fcc_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-fe75629d2952827e78801ee490a87fcc_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p data-pid=\"Jhp3Xl6S\">荷尔蒙阻断能够暂时拖延青春期的到来，在接受<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=444044435&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E8%8D%B7%E5%B0%94%E8%92%99%E9%98%BB%E6%96%AD%E5%89%82&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">荷尔蒙阻断剂<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>注射后，她不会有发育乳房，不会来月经。在一定程度上来说，这会给孩子足够的时间去思考是否想要变性。</p><p data-pid=\"8oS-dA5p\">希洛出生于2006年，是布拉德·皮特与安吉丽娜·朱莉共同生育的第一个孩子。作为世界巨星们的长女，从朱莉怀孕开始还在妈妈肚子里的希洛就受到了极大的关注。她的第一张照片以410万美元的天价卖给了《People》杂志，希洛也成为了世界上年龄最小的封面女郎。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-cb2e15635c7063d4cb3412f1091dd913_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"320\" data-rawheight=\"425\" data-original-token=\"v2-46decda7da86bf9c4b4fd059db494b25\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-227518315dfd34d56e85bb8ae17fb41a_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"320\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='320' height='425'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"320\" data-rawheight=\"425\" data-original-token=\"v2-46decda7da86bf9c4b4fd059db494b25\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-227518315dfd34d56e85bb8ae17fb41a_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"320\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-cb2e15635c7063d4cb3412f1091dd913_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p data-pid=\"K59Q61HO\"><b>你能接受女儿长大变成男孩吗？</b></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5bba2e27496430e43daedf541faea36d_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1028\" data-rawheight=\"560\" data-original-token=\"v2-9eae7e576f5ad6900b98081dc6bfa929\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-4f934dff33107d0f3df3877b7b1abf54_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1028\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-5bba2e27496430e43daedf541faea36d_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1028' height='560'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1028\" data-rawheight=\"560\" data-original-token=\"v2-9eae7e576f5ad6900b98081dc6bfa929\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-4f934dff33107d0f3df3877b7b1abf54_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1028\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-5bba2e27496430e43daedf541faea36d_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5bba2e27496430e43daedf541faea36d_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p data-pid=\"by2Hkfvt\"><b>一个人不仅有生理性别，而且有<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=444044435&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E6%80%A7%E5%88%AB&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">心理性别<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>。</b>根据美国心理学协会的研究结果，一个人的生理性别是根据染色体和性器官确定，而心理性别，是根据对性别相关的期望行为、角色和活动的社会建构来决定。心理性别与性别认同密切相关，是指人们对自己的认识，是作为男性、女性或是其他的感觉。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-13a480e09c4727794a42c1cae229eaeb_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1019\" data-rawheight=\"914\" data-original-token=\"v2-237acca5dd36634c15ac00f10faab200\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-273346e707eb535b29aea9317c00797c_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1019\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-13a480e09c4727794a42c1cae229eaeb_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1019' height='914'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1019\" data-rawheight=\"914\" data-original-token=\"v2-237acca5dd36634c15ac00f10faab200\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-273346e707eb535b29aea9317c00797c_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1019\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-13a480e09c4727794a42c1cae229eaeb_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-13a480e09c4727794a42c1cae229eaeb_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p></p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
